{"tid":2154031,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"想學投資股票","createTime":"2020-08-13T01:47:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T07:14:01.000Z","uid":154729,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"57384fff95b1c249d9f26493dabe267ae54ec036","tid":2154031,"uid":154729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T01:47:03.000Z","msg":"啱啱出黎做野 見而家武肺個市好似幾抵入<br />\n但本身又冇投資經驗<br />\n想學嘅話 可以點樣開始？"},{"pid":"f957187187e5b41e85502521bd9de93fcc802592","tid":2154031,"uid":36348,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T01:51:27.000Z","msg":"股票（英語：stock）或是資本存貨（英語：capital stock）是一種有價證券，股份有限公司將其所有權藉由這種有價證券進行分配[1]。因為股份有限公司需要籌措長期資金，因此將股票發給投資者作為公司資本部分所有權的憑證，成為股東以此獲得股息（股利），並分享公司成長或交易市場波動帶來的利潤；但也要共同承擔公司運作錯誤所帶來的風險。"},{"pid":"2d7741838a37446d03b4262939b7c28cc56d2a5f","tid":2154031,"uid":101328,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T01:52:21.000Z","msg":"all in 0005"},{"pid":"b7a2778e999168e82d40e8ce840c28870c431670","tid":2154031,"uid":123922,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T01:53:29.000Z","msg":"5仔低位呀"},{"pid":"115d931de3724d75b8b38235091d895e6f2597ad","tid":2154031,"uid":65711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T01:54:37.000Z","msg":"會唔會遲左6個月先開依個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"196b95cbd97fd949873138cf3a4404b76c4fb4f1","tid":2154031,"uid":5737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"115d931de3724d75b8b38235091d895e6f2597ad","tid":2154031,"uid":65711,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T01:54:37.000Z","msg":"會唔會遲左6個月先開依個post<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T01:56:19.000Z","msg":"咪係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢加都升返哂先黎入<br />\n想輸錢咩"},{"pid":"6869dfa22946a2002b4a2ff772afd190741a19c5","tid":2154031,"uid